name: Personalized Name Banner
description:
Last name banner shown on sage burlap. Measures approximately 6 1/2 feet long.

Custom Made Burlap Bunting Banner 
All banners are hand cut, sewn and painted.
Each banner is made of genuine burlap and sewn to real jute twine for an extra rustic look. 
These are a great addition to birthday parties, weddings, baby and bridal showers and are great for holiday and room décor. 

Each banner can be custom made to fit your personal style and color preference. Lettering can be done in a variety of fonts and colors and real glitter can always be added to the banner. Please contact me for with any questions or custom orders.
